CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 27, 1946, pg. 27, reads: "Shows skill at 'Y' - Here's Salem Ayoob, one of the district's most talented billiard champions, demonstrating his skill to a crowd of interested spectators at the Centre Avenue YMCA Tuesday night. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Salem Ayoob shooting pocket billiards with group of men looking on, in Centre Avenue YMCA
